            <div type="commentary">
                <p>The procurator who dedicated the epigraph on behalf of the inhabitants of Forum Claudii is not know by other texts. (B): ILS, Rémy - Ballet - Ferber: Z. 5: [Q(uintum)? Ael(ium)?] Malli[anum].</p>
